data.description: Don't Miss out!!This 5 bedroom, 3 1/2 bath home in the Walnut Gardens subdivision not only offers a comfortable and elegant living space but also the tranquility of a cove location and the convenience of being close to shopping, schools, and community amenities. Backyard features a covered patio that provides the perfect setting for outdoor relaxation and entertaining! Transferrable Home Warranty.
